---
#变量输出格式:
  rule:
    - you must output the update analysis and the actual update commands at once in the end of the next reply
    - the update commands works like the **JSON Patch (RFC 6902)** standard, must be a valid JSON array containing operation objects, but supports the following operations instead:
      - replace: replace the value of existing paths
      - delta: update the value of existing number paths by a delta value
      - insert: insert new items into an object or array (using `-` as array index intends appending to the end)
      - remove
    - don't update field names starts with `_` as they are readonly, such as `_变量`
  format: |-
    <content>
        ${此处为叙事正文，描绘天地灵气变化、宗门风云变幻、秘境异象显现、山河动荡与天地伟力。应以玄妙、磅礴、写意的文笔，展现万域界众生百态、天地大道运行、因果业力轮转。必须写出当前场景中所有角色的心理活动，但严禁描写{{user}}的心理。严禁在正文中使用【】符号，严禁插入旁白吐槽。}
    </content>
    <UpdateVariable>
    <Analysis>$(IN 简体中文, no more than 80 words)
    - ${calculate time passed: ...}
    - ${decide whether dramatic updates are allowed as it's in a special case or the time passed is more than usual: yes/no}
    - ${analyze every variable based on its corresponding `check`, according only to current reply instead of previous plots: ...}
    </Analysis>
    <JSONPatch>
    [
      // === General Format Reference (通用格式参考，**具体则参考下述变量更新规则**) ===
      { "op": "replace", "path": "/path/to/variable", "value": "new_value" },
      { "op": "delta", "path": "/path/to/number/variable", "value": -10 },
      { "op": "insert", "path": "/path/to/object/new_key", "value": { "new_data": "..." } },
      { "op": "insert", "path": "/path/to/array/-", "value": { "new_item": "..." } },
      { "op": "remove", "path": "/path/to/object/key" },


      // === Specific & Complex Examples (具体复杂示例) ===

      // Example 1: Inserting a new NPC. 'value' MUST be a complete object matching the getNpcSchema.
      // 示例1：插入一个新角色。'value' 必须是符合角色结构定义的完整对象，所有字段都需填充。
      {"op":"insert","path":"/交际网络/人物/林婉儿","value":{"身份":"青云宗内门弟子","宗门":"青云宗","性别":"女","种族":"人族","境界":"炼气七层","当前寿元":28,"寿元上限":120,"姓名":"林婉儿","身高":"身形窈窕","灵根":"上品木灵根","功法":"长春功","法宝":"青叶法剑","关系类型":"相识","好感度":20,"爱情值":0,"亲密度":10,"舒适度":60,"与人物关系":"主角在宗门认识的师姐, 为人热心。","描述标签":"热心肠|师姐|丹道天才","外貌描述":"着一袭淡绿罗裙，长发及腰，眉眼温婉如画，嘴角总是带着一丝若有若无的笑意。","背景故事":"出身于一个修仙世家，自小被寄予厚望，在丹道上颇有天赋。","其他":{}}},

      // Example 2: Updating an existing character's attributes.
      // 示例2：更新一个已存在角色的属性。
      { "op": "delta", "path": "/交际网络/人物/林婉儿/好感度", "value": 5 },
      { "op": "replace", "path": "/交际网络/人物/林婉儿/关系类型", "value": "朋友" },

      // Example 3: Inserting a new item (Gongfa/Fabao/Item) into the inventory. The key should be the item's name.
